headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Weeny Issi Classic & Vapid Flash GT
content: Fresh onto the asphalt of San Andreas, here are two pocket-size masterpieces to convince you once and for all that size doesn’t matter. One is the most concentrated dose of hipster fuel ever to top the most wanted list, while the other’s power-to-size ratio makes it the closest thing to driving an armor-piercing bullet.
